<p>
EO.Web Splitter offers the following features:
</p>
<ul>
    <li>Dividing screen into multiple panes and allow user to resize the panes;</li>
    <li>Supports both <b>Horizontal</b> and <b>Vertical</b> layout;</li>
    <li>Supports <b>Nesting</b> in order to implement complex layout;</li>
    <li>Supports <b>Auto Fill</b> mode to automatically resize when browser window resizes;</li>
    <li>Supports <b>Splitter Buttons</b> to collapse/expand pane with a single click;</li>
</ul>
